*Issue 1: Unable to remove Invoice amount completely & add it in edit mode*

User is in INV>Orders & Receipts>Receipts

{color:#ff5630}User tries to remove the Invoice amount and user unable to remove and add the amount properly which is not correct{color}

{color:#36b37e}Expected Result: User should be able to remove the Invoice amount & add it properly.{color}



*Issue 2: Receipt amount is changing in view mode, if we open the edit screen for the second time* 

User is in INV>Orders & Receipts>Receipts

User saves the edit screen and reopens the edit screen and saves it.

{color:#ff5630}Then user opens the view receipt and observes amount is changing, amount in edit screen & view screen are different which is not correct{color}

{color:#36b37e}Expected Result: Invoice amount should be same in edit screen & view receipt screen.{color}



*Isse 3: Need to add , (Comma) in Receipts Summary page for Receipt Amount field*

User is in INV>Orders & Receipts>Receipts

User saves the receipt and comes to the receipt summary screen

{color:#ff5630}Then user observes if Receipt amount is 1775.15, (Comma) is missing for the amount{color}

{color:#36b37e}Expected Result: Receipt amount should show like 1,775.15{color}



