NXT-68157.desc:
*Merged Orders are not displaying in the distribution orders*
User is in INV>Distribution

User has already created an order for Nov 11th 2025 which is in Unassigned

Then user creates a new order and merges with the existing order and opens the Distribution

{color:#ff5630}Then user observes the second order which is merged is not showing in the distribution which is not correct{color}

{color:#36b37e}Expected Result: Merged second order should be displayed in the Distribution.{color}
